pays
so
much
and
the
other
pays
more
.
###
We
just
do
n't
have
that
kind
of
income
stream
.
''
###
All
this
is
causing
convulsions
in
professional
football
.
###
Owners
,
largely
complacent
in
the
past
,
are
now
almost
