.
###
The
bill
would
``
divert
scarce
resources
of
the
commission
away
from
broker-dealers
into
areas
which
simply
have
no
way
of
affecting
broker-dealers
,
''
Mr.
Raoul-Duval
said
.
###
Sources
in
the
industry
and
on
Capitol
Hill
say
a
compromise
that
would
placate
the
industry
while
addressing
the
SEC
's
