in
that
-LCB-
UAL
-RCB-
deal
,
''
he
said
.
###
``
They
are
becoming
more
independent
.
###
It
's
a
sound
phenomenon
.
''
###
Sanwa
Bank
Ltd.
is
one
Japanese
bank
that
decided
not
to
participate
in
the
first
UAL
