.
###
Roe
vs.
Wade
was
the
Supreme
Court
's
1973
decision
that
recognized
a
woman
's
right
to
abortion
.
###
Mario
Mandina
,
president
of
Kansas
City
Lawyers
for
Life
,
says
that
if
abortion
foes
succeed
in
using
the
preamble
to
escape
