.
''
###
That
would
be
an
ironic
result
of
a
case
in
which
the
Supreme
Court
expressly
stopped
short
of
overruling
Roe
vs.
Wade
.
###
In
two
other
cases
,
the
possible
consequences
of
the
Supreme
Court
ruling
appear
even
more
unintended
.
###
In
