.
###
In
terms
of
sheer
brutality
,
the
Somali
regime
of
Siad
Barre
may
rank
as
No.
1
in
the
world
.
###
The
only
reason
that
Somalia
remains
in
obscurity
is
numbers
:
a
sparsely
populated
wasteland
of
8.5
million
people
spread
out
over
an
expanse
nearly
the
size
of
Texas
.
###
The
Barre
dictatorship
simply
is
limited
in
the
amount
of
people
it
can
torture
and
kill
.
###
Beheading
small
children
,
stabbing
elderly
people
to
death
,
raping
and
shooting
women
,
and
burying
people
