###
OPEC
's
ability
to
produce
more
petroleum
than
it
can
sell
is
beginning
to
cast
a
shadow
over
world
oil
markets
.
###
Output
from
the
Organization
of
Petroleum
Exporting
Countries
is
already
at
a
high
for
the
year
and
most
member
nations
are
running
flat
out
.
###
But
