of
about
20
%
in
Lonrho
PLC
.
###
However
,
Bond
Corp.
said
the
tax
benefits
remain
available
and
might
be
used
later
.
###
Earnings
before
interest
and
tax
from
brewing
dived
50
%
to
A$
123.8
million
from
A$
247.3
million
.
###
The
company
said
the
general
