funds
last
week
.
###
``
There
certainly
has
n't
been
a
panic
reaction
,
''
said
Steven
Norwitz
,
a
vice
president
at
T.
Rowe
Price
Associates
.
###
People
showed
some
staying
power
and
,
in
fact
,
interest
in
buying
equities
.
''
###
Source
:
