environment
.
###
They
're
more
worried
about
bread
on
the
table
.
###
Pittston
Co.
's
third-quarter
net
income
plunged
79
%
,
reflecting
the
impact
of
a
prolonged
and
bitter
labor
strike
at
its
coal
operations
.
###
Net
sank
to
$
3.1
million
,
or
eight
cents
a
share
,
including
$
789,000
,
or
two
cents
a
share
,
reflecting
a
tax-loss
carry-forward
.
###
In
the
year-ago
quarter
,
net
totaled
$
14.7
million
,
or
38
cents
a
share
,
including
$
4
million
,
or
10
cents
a
share
,
reflecting
a
tax-loss
carry-forward
.
###
Revenue
slipped
0.7
%
to
$
395.3
million
from
$
398.3
million
.
###
Pittston
also
owns
Brink
's
Inc.
,
the
security
service
,
and
Burlington
Air
Express
,
the
