should
he
become
New
York
's
first
black
mayor
.
###
Ordinarily
,
a
clever
opponent
would
find
a
way
to
capitalize
on
the
other
side
's
misfortunes
.
###
But
Mr.
Giuliani
,
a
celebrated
prosecutor
,
has
had
difficulty
switching
from
his
crime-busting
,
