official
in
Massachusetts
said
Clean
Harbors
Inc.
's
environmental-impact
statement
for
a
proposed
incinerator
in
Braintree
was
inadequate
.
###
The
official
,
John
DeVillars
,
asked
Clean
Harbors
for
more
information
before
ruling
on
a
permit
for
