.
###
Net
was
$
3.1
million
,
or
16
cents
a
share
,
up
from
$
1.6
million
,
or
nine
cents
a
share
.
###
Revenue
was
$
41.2
million
,
up
from
$
27.5
million
.
###
For
the
nine
months
,
net
was
$
7.7
million
,
or
41
cents
a
share
,
up
97
%
from
$
3.9
million
,
or
22
cents
a
