at
Nomura
Research
Institute
.
###
``
If
there
is
another
bad
trade
number
,
there
could
be
an
awful
lot
of
pressure
,
''
noted
Simon
Briscoe
,
U.K.
economist
for
Midland
Montagu
,
a
unit
of
Midland
Bank
PLC
.
###
Forecasts
for
the
trade
figures
range
widely
,
but
few
economists
expect
the
data
to
show
a
very
marked
