pound
.
###
Meanwhile
,
overall
evidence
on
the
economy
remains
fairly
clouded
.
###
In
his
Mansion
House
speech
,
Mr.
Lawson
warned
that
a
further
slowdown
can
be
expected
as
the
impact
of
the
last
