Ron
Brierley
raised
its
stake
in
the
company
Friday
to
15.02
%
from
about
14.6
%
Thursday
and
from
13.7
%
the
previous
week
.
###
I.E.P.
Securities
Ltd.
,
a
unit
of
Mr.
Brierley
's
Hong
Kong-based
Industrial
Equity
-LRB-
Pacific
-RRB-
Ltd.
,
boosted
its
holdings
in
Vickers
to
38.8
million
shares
.
###
The
latest
purchase
follows
small
increases
in
his
holdings
made
over
the
past
five
months
.
###
In
May
,
Mr.
Brierley
's
stake
shrank
to
8.7
%
after
ranging
between
9
%
and
11
%
for
