.
''
###
Newport
Beach
operations
differ
from
the
Hollywood
boiler
rooms
in
style
as
well
as
in
dollars
.
###
Traditionally
,
boiler
rooms
operate
on
the
cheap
,
since
few
,
if
any
,
customers
ever
visit
their
