.
###
``
It
's
traders
squaring
positions
.
###
's
not
good
;
the
market
is
setting
up
for
another
fall
.
''
###
Indeed
,
many
traders
said
that
uncertainty
about
today
's
monthly
expiration
of
stocks-index
futures
and
options
,
and
options
on
individual
