,
prompted
a
lot
of
buying
by
speculative
traders
who
were
unwinding
positions
that
were
bets
on
declining
stock
prices
.
###
The
number
of
outstanding
contracts
in
the
October
Major
Market
Index
jumped
from
5,273
on
Friday
to
9,023
on
